name: If it ain't Baroque, don't fix it
author: Digi
description:
Swathed
 in warm tones, this palette is perfect for capturing dynamic lighting 
in the dreamy style of your favorite baroque frescoes. Gentle greens 
with warmer highlights and slightly cooler lowlights coupled with the 
pops of contrast can capture a garden so decadent that you'll feel 
transported to an Oscar Wilde novel.
